German chancellor comments during
panel discussion in Berlin.
* Merkel responds to write-in question on how she reacts to
protester portrayals with Hitler moustache
* Struggling euro-area countries shouldn’t look for scapegoats:
Merkel
* “I take it in stride and it doesn’t change my work,” Merkel
says
